{
  "stem": "10905.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'd say three months, two or three months, not-- maximum.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's mother was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was not-- The only people who were in Belgrade, I think, was my mother's younger brother, my mother, my father, my sister, and I.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father, of course, went in the Army at the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was just the-- there was just the four of us from our immediate family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The rest of our entire family lived in Subotica, was in the town or in the neighborhood in the area.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to cross a border, of course, from Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where we went across the river on rafts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know exactly when, where and exactly how, but that's-- that's how we did it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, we had to, of course, after the car got shot up, we had to abandon our car.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have a car any longer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you had to sneak across the border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, there was-- the war was fluid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had just started.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was really just starting then at that-- in that part of the world.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the crossing over was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] illegal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, there were always people-- there are no borders that cannot be crossed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have to have God, you have to have money, you have to have pull, you have to luck.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my-- my-- primarily, my memories were very, very fond.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're very nice memories, living in Subotica, you know, during the first part of the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- we lived there, I think, perhaps, till 1943-- for two years, 1943.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have to go to school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was a young kid.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
